        },
        "content-2": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "headphone",
            "heading": "<em>Customer Support</em>",
            "text": "<p>Our friendly customer service team is ready to help with your Spa or order questions.</p><p>Email us At: <a href=\"mailto:support@waveglobal.com\" title=\"mailto:support@wavespas.com\">support@wavespas.com</a></p><p><strong>Monday to Friday: 8:30am – 5:30pm</strong></p><p><strong>Saturday: 8:00am – 4:00pm</strong></p><p>We aim to reply within <strong>8 working hours</strong>, so you’ll never be left waiting too long. If you message us outside these hours, no worries - we’ll dive right back in as soon as we’re back online. </p><p>Thanks for your patience and for being part of our community <br/></p>",
            "highlighted_text": "text",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle",
            "color_text": "#171717",
            "color_background": "#f9f9f9",
